the numerical method developed in the previous section. In fact, we try
to show that
limℎ→0‖‖𝑌 (𝑛ℎ) − 𝑌𝑛‖‖ = 0,
 𝑛ℎ = 𝑡 fixed, (43)
which means the solution of the approximate set of equations converges
to that of the exact problem as the step-length ℎ goes to 0.
